                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190915-65-off341 t18190915-65-cd342"></join>, one watch, value 20 s.; one seal, value 10 s, and one key, value 2 s. 6 d., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18190915-65-victim591" type="victimName">
